'''''N''-甲酰基哌啶'''是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>11</sub>NO。它可用作极性非质子溶剂，比其它酰胺溶剂（如[[二甲基甲酰胺|DMF]]）有更好的烃类溶解性。<ref>{{cite book |title=Kirk‑Othmer Encyclopedia of Chemical Technology |chapter=Pyridine and Pyridine Derivatives |author1=Eric F. V. Scriven  |author2=Ramiah Murugan  |year=2005<!-- |name-list-style=amp -->|publisher=Wiley |doi=10.1002/0471238961.1625180919031809.a01.pub2|isbn=0471238961 }}</ref>它可用于将甲酰基转移至[[格氏试剂|格氏试剂]]：<ref>{{OrgSynth | collvol = 7 | collvolpages = 451 | prep = cv7p0451 | title = Formyl Transfer to Grignard Reagents with ''N''-Formylpiperidine: 3-Phenylpropionaldehyde | author = [[George_Andrew_Olah|George Andrew Olah]] and Massoud Arvanaghi}}</ref>

: PhCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>MgCl + C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>11</sub>NO → PhCH<sub>2</sub>CH<sub>2</sub>CHO

在一些烷基锂化合物的甲酰化反应中，使用''N''-甲酰基哌啶比DMF有更高的产率。<ref>{{cite journal |author1=Lidija Bondarenko |author2=Ina Dix |author3=Heino Hinrichs |author4=Henning Hopf | title = Cyclophanes. Part LII:1 Ethynyl[2.2]paracyclophanes – New Building Blocks for Molecular Scaffolding | journal = [[Synthesis_(journal)|Synthesis]] | volume = 2004| issue = 16 | pages = 2751–2759 | year = 2004 | doi = 10.1055/s-2004-834872}}</ref>

